1. As a user, I need to be able to join a game using an ID.

2. As a host, I need to be able to start the game once atleast one other player has joined.

3. As a player, I need to be able to enter the price of an item for guessing.

4. As a host, I need the option to play again or quit once the results have been shown

5. As a player, I need to see who won each game.

6. As a player, I want to see a picture, title, and description of the item I am guessing on

